exchange.name: Australia-Indonesia Youth Exchange Program (AIYEP)
exchange.description: Every year the AIYEP program sends 18 young Indonesians aged 21-25 to Australia for two months (October to December) where they take part in work placements, cultural performances, homestays and visits to local schools and communities.
